                    </div>
                    <span>This book works better as an introduction to Buddhism than many popularly available introductions.<p>A personal selection of well translated material from a real scholar.<p>It is hard to avoid going back to particular sections for pleasure and reference again and again.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Excellent book. Perfect selection of writings.</div>
